      "line": 84,
      "message": "We should not assume that CLAMP will be sending us \"Restart\" vs \"restart\" vs \"RESTART\". I have run into problems with this internally. I know internally they send \"restart\" but I think it is safer for us if Policy takes the recipe and sets the casing so this switch statement doesn't go to default and we don't run into any issues",
